descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 30 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
# What's New:

💥**4-PLAYER SQUADS & 10-PLAYER LOBBIES ARE LIVE!**

💥**FULL & DEMO GAME PLAYERS LINK!**

Dive into a **thrilling dungeon adventure** with **physics-based combat and endless arenas.**        
[media]
**discord.gg/pdvr** join to win gifts🎁

# 🕌Mega Size Update!  10-Player Lobbies & 4-Player Squads 
- **Massive Lobbies**: **10-Player Lobbies are now live**. Bring all your friends, jump into the dungeon chaos!
- **Bigger Squads**: Strategize with your **4-player squads**! More friends, more fun, more power! 
- **Random Maps**: Every run is different, filled with traps, treasure boxes, and unexpected surprises.
[media]

# 🤝Play with Anyone: Full & Demo Game Link 
- **Seamless Co-op** : Full and Demo game players are linked. Full game owners can host their friends who haven't purchased the full game yet to explore the entire dungeon together! 

# 💥Epic Boss Battles, 2nd Stage Power-Up
- **4 Bosses to Conquer**: Skull King slashes his axe. Ghost Lord shoots bullets that chase you. Fight them!
- **Second Stage**: Angel becomes a giant eye monster, firing deadly lasers that burn the ground beneath you. God of Time shatters the ground, forcing everyone into a new arena —battles upgrade are so exciting!
[media]
# ⚔️Rich Weapons
- Engage in **challenging physical combat** with shieds, claws and bows.
- Choose from Katana, wands, and more—each with **unique effects**!
- Use **BOSS Weapons** to crush bosses and feel power!
[media]

# 👑Create Your Hero 
-  The Witcher, Black Knight, Bird Man...classic & creative heroes to choose!

[media]
